{"tid":607226,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"fb登報道歉　同日爆收集手機私隱","createTime":"2018-03-27T06:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T06:35:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"538ece133a227f9c10b98055c6b3a3e0309b0b11","tid":607226,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:30:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180327/20344152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180327%2F20344152&d=NrUMFqPQK8uRPtOwRQLeh5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=ed8dc025\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180327%2F20344152&h=dce16467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180327/20344152</a><br />\n<br />\nfb登報道歉　同日爆收集手機私隱<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180327/large/27wk8p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180327%2Flarge%2F27wk8p.jpg&h=3403a2f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nfb在《紐約時報》刊登道歉啟事。<br />\n<br />\nfacebook被揭縱容「劍橋分析」不當收集用戶數據後，行政總裁朱克伯格前日在英美多份報章刊登全版道歉啟事，承認「違背了信任，fb正採取措施確保不重蹈覆轍」。豈料同日再被爆出一直從Android手機收集聯絡人姓名、手機號碼、通話及短訊聯絡紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱為排列聯絡人次序<br />\n<br />\n不少用戶都是在決定永久刪除fb時，下載賬戶內的全部數據，才驚見fb所掌握的資料遠比想像中多，新西蘭軟件開發員麥凱直言感到「心寒」。對此，fb解釋獲取聯絡人及通訊紀錄，是為了排列Messager聯絡人的次序，方便用戶找到朋友，用戶可自行選擇是否容許fb收集這些數據。fb又指，這些資料不會轉售予第三方，而之前收集的通話及短訊歷史將被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n另外，在事件中濫用fb數據的「劍橋分析」，再被踢爆2014年派出至少20名非美國籍員工赴美為共和黨助選，違反選舉法中外國人不得「直接或間接參與」政治活動決策過程的規例。在一浪接一浪醜聞打擊下，用戶對fb失去信心，路透社及易普索的民調指，僅41%美國人相信fb按照法律保護用戶個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/路透社"},{"pid":"966f6ac18483a46b2a06b6a28af1c8b45613b218","tid":607226,"uid":20805,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:33:25.000Z","msg":"喺亞洲地區呢一樣嘢叫大數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5322856237569cc17d260c2ca1ace7d94eb2d502","tid":607226,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:35:03.000Z","msg":"幾日前新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}